[ INFO] [1487623980.286334087, 4.635000000]: Starting JVM with arguments: -Djava.class.path=ValkyrieController.jar -XX:+UseSerialGC -Xmx4g -Xms4g -XX:NewSize=3g -XX:MaxNewSize=3g -XX:CompileThreshold=1000 -verbosegc -Djava.library.path=lib/

Cannot find class us/ihmc/valkyrieRosControl/ValkyrieRosControlController
